videos.description: Asia Durr hits her third 3 of the first quarter to put the Cardinals up early.
videos.headline: Louisville's Durr drills it from deep

videos.description: Louisvile's Myisha Hines-Allen blows by her defender and gets the bucket with and an up-and-under finish.
videos.headline: Hines-Allen shows off with a crossover and scoop layup

videos.description: Jazmine Jones finishes through the contact to get the tough bucket off the glass.
videos.headline: Jones finishes the and-1 layup

videos.description: Louisville's Asia Durr uses her sweet stroke to nail a 3 at the buzzer, her 8th three of the game.
videos.headline: Durr beats the buzzer, drops 34 through 3 quarters

videos.description: Rebecca Lobo talks with Louisville's Myisha Hines-Allen and Asia Durr after their blowout win against No. 2 Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Hines-Allen and Durr combine for 67 points
